{"tid":1799032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12.26 和理SHOP檢討","createTime":"2019-12-26T15:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T04:15:51.000Z","uid":282534,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8e3f999436d224158674d43e8a31b76447389b42","tid":1799032,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"和理SHOP檢討<br />\n<br />\n今日大家都做得好好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但moko防暴入場之前我有所保留<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nmoko今次係個賭注  <br />\n大家賭佢唔會濫捕<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔排除下次換左指揮官會發din <br />\n結果咬晒全部人 <br />\n唔係無呢個可能性<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再有一點就係  如果要撤離 <br />\n大家一定唔好拖好最後一刻先走<br />\n特別係唔熟地勢既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為你搵路都要時間<br />\n同埋人群要散去同樣須要時間<br />\n所以預留空間俾自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過 結果論  <br />\n今日成本比早兩日低好多!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理SHOP必須以低成本持之以效<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9f44a3471763957f045faaeecf066be0b995a0","tid":1799032,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d85045a64e0fb194258a5af4327723af036474","tid":1799032,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:54:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHQ%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=3d1b682b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66916ab47b41a9cbf8856be42d57c80f26c4938","tid":1799032,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:56:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21df0cf371fa6b1bf6856271ab7277b3b4d24a84","tid":1799032,"uid":1212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:56:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"faaea0fda7090124637d78fc70cdf916305c7802","tid":1799032,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:56:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3c70ac26f61597eabcd743e641f8197a1fe3bfdd","tid":1799032,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:56:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b3bc79cef2f432ba916ea2100f692c1db3eb4d4","tid":1799032,"uid":148355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:57:39.000Z","msg":"同意。當取得一定成果就要收割離場。"},{"pid":"df7ad7c09321a9d68fa93293a5641e336284f41d","tid":1799032,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:57:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d587307436aeb67ffa25820c34476e0c72699e04","tid":1799032,"uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:59:59.000Z","msg":"我唔建議入藍舖玩<br />\n呢兩日入完藍舖都出事"},{"pid":"a1c7badd9dc35308f9f31d00362cf6a23d6202d0","tid":1799032,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:00:20.000Z","msg":"但班狗用公眾地方行為不檢去濫捕點捕？<br />\n我理解叫口號唱歌佢用呢條罪都拉得"},{"pid":"765660892cce0d399dadb078ee582a636a15a2c6","tid":1799032,"uid":138134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1c7badd9dc35308f9f31d00362cf6a23d6202d0","tid":1799032,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:00:20.000Z","msg":"但班狗用公眾地方行為不檢去濫捕點捕？<br />\n我理解叫口號唱歌佢用呢條罪都拉得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:00:42.000Z","msg":"入到黎唔好出聲"},{"pid":"b551b822c33abf99c37b526c2d144fc4173d9a3f","tid":1799032,"uid":138134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:01:18.000Z","msg":"衣著要正常唔好太sharp"},{"pid":"550ac5a5e8203ee923b063f4e3823b796cd3de4b","tid":1799032,"uid":253223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d587307436aeb67ffa25820c34476e0c72699e04","tid":1799032,"uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:59:59.000Z","msg":"我唔建議入藍舖玩<br />\n呢兩日入完藍舖都出事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:01:22.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實係門口 嗌口號已經見效"},{"pid":"e759a96ea688d618ccc3c61f631a539ae325a0d4","tid":1799032,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:02:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"919fa37f6a903128486dc8eeedd5776c96c44766","tid":1799032,"uid":109345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:03:07.000Z","msg":"其實整體黎講<br />\n和你shop比街頭抗爭可以<br />\n更快攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n少人被捕 （唔會好似一日幾百人，絕大部分係濫捕）<br />\n至少性質唔會係暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n堅持繼續做<br />\n<br />\n但要改善地方：<br />\n1. 小心便衣 尤其裝修手足<br />\n2. 隨時可能比人check身分 袋<br />\n3. 可能被包圍<br />\n4. 街坊/blaclblock 裝要視乎情況<br />\n5. 適量簡單文具<br />\n6. 和你shop商場可以轉 唔洗每次都單一幾個<br />\n7. 有需要時 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">跟隊 保護手足</span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"1ca2f4ccab150052557a530820aedd190c205803","tid":1799032,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"765660892cce0d399dadb078ee582a636a15a2c6","tid":1799032,"uid":138134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1c7badd9dc35308f9f31d00362cf6a23d6202d0","tid":1799032,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:00:20.000Z","msg":"但班狗用公眾地方行為不檢去濫捕點捕？<br />\n我理解叫口號唱歌佢用呢條罪都拉得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:00:42.000Z","msg":"入到黎唔好出聲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:03:26.000Z","msg":"點樣唔出聲<br />\n都要叫口號架"},{"pid":"b14db1e9c3be163fd854d18919d8fc9feb55eeee","tid":1799032,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:04:36.000Z","msg":"#28Dec #元朗 #天水圍 #集會 #中學生<br />\n元朗區中學生集會- 延續革命 毋忘初心<br />\n(聯署721 滅不了的連儂牆聲音 學生抗爭心聲) <br />\n日期 : 12月28日 (六)<br />\n時間：19:30-21:30<br />\n地點：天水圍 銀座<br />\n自備：memo紙<br />\n✅已獲發不反對通知書<br />\n公海 : <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/KwqxNxX0iDxvH4rGWczmlA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FKwqxNxX0iDxvH4rGWczmlA&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHQ%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=d88ad7f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/KwqxNxX0iDxvH4rGWczmlA</a>"},{"pid":"f1fe0760a3c9944f8204833c4e671f555e16f634","tid":1799032,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:05:22.000Z","msg":"留意到銅記商場從未被衝入<br />\n點解會咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2703bc7ecdf0d8a6dbc1bfb7a643a4b4e0a2444d","tid":1799032,"uid":309948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e98eb61e841bd04d6438e2db43b60de05b6472","tid":1799032,"uid":138134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ca2f4ccab150052557a530820aedd190c205803","tid":1799032,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"765660892cce0d399dadb078ee582a636a15a2c6","tid":1799032,"uid":138134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1c7badd9dc35308f9f31d00362cf6a23d6202d0","tid":1799032,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:00:20.000Z","msg":"但班狗用公眾地方行為不檢去濫捕點捕？<br />\n我理解叫口號唱歌佢用呢條罪都拉得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:00: